code: @Override protected final void assertFromXContent(T aggregation, ParsedAggregation parsedAggregation) {     assertTrue(parsedAggregation instanceof PercentileRanks).     PercentileRanks parsedPercentileRanks = (PercentileRanks) parsedAggregation.     for (Percentile percentile : aggregation) {         Double value = percentile.getValue().         assertEquals(aggregation.percent(value), parsedPercentileRanks.percent(value), 0).         assertEquals(aggregation.percentAsString(value), parsedPercentileRanks.percentAsString(value)).     }     Class<? extends ParsedPercentiles> parsedClass = implementationClass().     assertTrue(parsedClass != null && parsedClass.isInstance(parsedAggregation)). }
@Override protected void assertPercentile(T agg, Double value) {     assertThat(agg.percent(value), equalTo(Double.NaN)).     assertThat(agg.percentAsString(value), equalTo("NaN")). }
